Package de.cuioss.test.jsf.producer

package de.cuioss.test.jsf.producer
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    JsfObjectsProducer
    Various JSF Producers for junit tests.
    ServletMockObjectsProducer
    Produces a RequestScoped HttpServletResponse RequestScoped HttpServletRequest. Dependent ServletContext In contrast to ServletObjectsFromJSFContextProducer the mocks are instantiated directly It is designed as 'opt-in'.
    ServletObjectsFromJSFContextProducer
    Produces a RequestScoped HttpServletResponse RequestScoped HttpServletRequest. Dependent ServletContext The objects are derived from the FacesContext It is designed as 'opt-in'.
